amic API or static fallback)\n5. OpenPGP signature verification confirms the manifest wasn't tampered with\n6. File hashes in the manifest are verified against actual plugin files\n7. During validation, `ValidateSignature()` checks the signature status\n8. For unsigned plugins, `UnsignedPluginAuthorizer.CanLoadPlugin()` checks the allowlist\n9. Unsigned plugins not in the allowlist are prevented from loading\n"
